app.handler

Enum Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Status>
      • app.handler.Status
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Status> 

    public enum Status
extends java.lang.Enum<Status>
    This enum represents the status of an IHandlerResponse.
    The status codes are based on the HTTP status codes.
